{"tid":1802931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊間邊間黃店好難食 咁係咪藍店好好食你就去食？","createTime":"2019-12-29T22:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T08:54:21.000Z","uid":201604,"like":66,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c6229c9f5bf93d470abc7fed32909f0a097f6956","tid":1802931,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T22:31:06.000Z","msg":"答我 係定唔係？<br />\n我自己既答案就係<br />\n就算係幾撚好食既藍店我都唔撚會去食<br />\n<br />\n一路食一路聽住藍絲老闆伙記話支持警察打死手足<br />\n你會食得安心？<br />\n<br />\n至於黃店好唔好食 試過一次就知<br />\n唔鍾意咪去第間<br />\n除左出名黃店 仲有好多唔出名既黃店等大家支持<br />\n肚餓時打開黃藍地圖<br />\n每間都試下 岩胃口咪下次再幫襯<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔岩胃口咪幫襯第二間黃店囉<br />\n總之我就係唔會去藍店 吹呀？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e39a38fee1bad97494de80955a337bb95e4555bd","tid":1802931,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T22:31:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"109e6214ace9f9cd83f0d31ff23d26cec447b72e","tid":1802931,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T22:37:54.000Z","msg":"想知邊啲藍店好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4293249354942dd65457bfb35725f8aa0d3a5300","tid":1802931,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"109e6214ace9f9cd83f0d31ff23d26cec447b72e","tid":1802931,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T22:37:54.000Z","msg":"想知邊啲藍店好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T22:40:40.000Z","msg":"元氣啲薑好食 淨食薑0蚊埋單"},{"pid":"9a4b0152f3058e2161e69ff37fe936d1fd6a090b","tid":1802931,"uid":103189,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"109e6214ace9f9cd83f0d31ff23d26cec447b72e","tid":1802931,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T22:37:54.000Z","msg":"想知邊啲藍店好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T22:40:53.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣 為食龍<br />\n日本野，飯團，定食，壽司"},{"pid":"831e537e9c6ce799